itional properties to get for each category:\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-paramvalue-prop-sortkey','s:96:\"Adds the sortkey (hexadecimal string) and sortkey prefix (human-readable part) for the category.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-paramvalue-prop-timestamp','s:46:\"Adds timestamp of when the category was added.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-paramvalue-prop-hidden','s:72:\"Tags categories that are hidden with <code>_&#95;HIDDENCAT_&#95;</code>.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-param-show','s:33:\"Which kind of categories to show.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-param-limit','s:30:\"How many categories to return.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-param-categories','s:96:\"Only list these categories. Useful for checking whether a certain page is in a certain category.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-param-dir','s:31:\"The direction in which to list.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-example-simple','s:72:\"Get a list of categories the page <kbd>Albert Einstein</kbd> belongs to.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categories-example-generator','s:81:\"Get information about all categories used in the page <kbd>Albert Einstein</kbd>.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categoryinfo-description','s:47:\"Returns information about the given categories.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categoryinfo-example-simple','s:74:\"Get information about <kbd>Category:Foo</kbd> and <kbd>Category:Bar</kbd>.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categorymembers-description','s:35:\"List all pages in a given category.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categorymembers-param-title','s:142:\"Which category to enumerate (required). Must include the <kbd>{{ns:category}}:</kbd> prefix. Cannot be used together with <var>$1pageid</var>.\";'),('de','messages:apihelp-query+categorymembers-param-pageid','s:86:\"Page ID of the category to enumerate. Cannot be used together with <var>$1tit